            "id": "https://codingfxj.github.io/2021/04/10/HEXO%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/",
            "url": "https://codingfxj.github.io/2021/04/10/HEXO%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/",
            "title": "HEXO搭建博客笔记",
            "date_published": "2021-04-10T14:46:32.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h3 id=\"前言\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#前言\">#</a> 前言</h3>\n<p>​\t\t\t\t\t经过了这两天的折腾，作为菜鸟的我，也终于搭好了一个自己的个人博客（Github 与 Hexo 的结合）。</p>\n<p>然后今天想着，趁着把之昨天的操作、那些踩过的坑等等再整理一下，免得到时候忘了，又得去找教程。</p>\n<h3 id=\"所需的软件和平台\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#所需的软件和平台\">#</a> 所需的软件和平台</h3>\n<h4 id=\"必须的软件\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#必须的软件\">#</a> 必须的软件：</h4>\n<h6 id=\"nodejs\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#nodejs\">#</a> NODE.JS</h6>\n<h6 id=\"git\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#git\">#</a> GIT</h6>\n<h4 id=\"可选的软件\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#可选的软件\">#</a> 可选的软件：</h4>\n<h6 id=\"visual-studio-code\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#visual-studio-code\">#</a> Visual Studio Code</h6>\n<h6 id=\"typora\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#typora\">#</a> TYPORA</h6>\n<h3 id=\"要用到的框架或平台\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#要用到的框架或平台\">#</a> 要用到的框架或平台：</h3>\n<h5 id=\"hexo\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#hexo\">#</a> HEXO</h5>\n<h5 id=\"github\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#github\">#</a> Github</h5>\n<h3 id=\"安装说明\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#安装说明\">#</a> 安装说明</h3>\n<h5 id=\"nodejs和typoro-git一路选-next-就行了\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#nodejs和typoro-git一路选-next-就行了\">#</a> node.js 和 Typoro、Git，一路选 next 就行了。</h5>\n<h5 id=\"vscode安装好之后默认是英文界面可以在插件市场里搜索chinese安装之后重启软件变成中文版\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#vscode安装好之后默认是英文界面可以在插件市场里搜索chinese安装之后重启软件变成中文版\">#</a> VsCode 安装好之后默认是英文界面，可以在插件市场里搜索 chinese，安装之后重启软件，变成中文版。</h5>\n<h3 id=\"检验是否成功安装\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#检验是否成功安装\">#</a> 检验是否成功安装</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>用 Win + R 打开运行，输入 cmd 并进入 cmd 窗口，或者在右键打开 Git bash，输入命令。能看到版本号就表示成功啦。</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>node.js 的检查</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">node -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>npm 的检查 (NPM 是随同 NodeJS 一起安装的包管理工具，能解决 NodeJS 代码部署上的很多问题)。</strong></p>\n  <figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Git 的检查</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<img src=\"/images/image-20210521124138671.png\">\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"hexo的安装\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#hexo的安装\">#</a> HEXO 的安装</h3>\n<p><strong>在 Git bash 或者 CMD 界面执行命令</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>安装之前可以先设置一下淘宝镜像加速器</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install -g cnpm --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>全局安装框架</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>创建自己的博客目录</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo init 博客的文件夹名字</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>进入博客的目录</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> 博客的文件夹名字</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>复制文件到博客的目录</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>安装 Hexo 部署插件</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>请在博客的目录下启动 Git bash，再执行以下代码</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"git的配置\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#git的配置\">#</a> GIT 的配置</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>设置用户名称</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git config --global user.name <span class=\"string\">&quot;用户名&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>设置用户邮箱</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git config --global user.email <span class=\"string\">&quot;用户邮箱&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>生成密钥</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class=\"string\">&quot;用户邮箱&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>以上代码执行之后，会让你设置密码，推荐全都不要设置，直接连按三次回车键。</strong></p>\n<h3 id=\"github配置\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#github配置\">#</a> Github 配置</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>创建一个仓库，名为：自己用户名 + .github.io</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/223E7A465293.png.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>配置 SSH key，复制生成的密钥（在 C:\\Users\\admin\\.ssh\\id_rsa.pub 文件里），</strong></p>\n<h6 id=\"githubsettingssh-and-gpg-keys-new-ssh-keys粘贴并添加ssh-keys\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#githubsettingssh-and-gpg-keys-new-ssh-keys粘贴并添加ssh-keys\">#</a> Github—&gt;Setting—&gt;SSH and GPG keys —&gt;new SSH keys，粘贴并添加 SSH keys。</h6>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"博客-_configyml-文件的配置\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#博客-_configyml-文件的配置\">#</a> 博客 _config.yml 文件的配置</h3>\n<p><strong>打开博客根目录的 _config.yml 文件，将一下信息添加到里面去。</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">url: https://CodingFXJ.github.io</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20210521130458570.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><strong>【注意】+ 博客根目录的 _config.yml 文件，和主题根目录的 _config.yml 文件，冒号后面有个空格！</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">deploy:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"built_in\">type</span>: git</span><br><span class=\"line\">  repo: https://github.com/CodingFXJ/CodingFXJ.github.io.git <span class=\"comment\">#替换成自己仓库的HTTP URL地址</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  branch: main</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"hexo常用代码\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#hexo常用代码\">#</a> <a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/configuration.html\">HEXO 常用代码</a></h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><strong>清理缓存，会自动删除博客目录下得 public 文件。(hexo cl 是 hexo clean 的简写)</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo cl <span class=\"comment\">#或者hexo clean</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<img src=\"/images/image-20210521131113813.png\">\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>生成静态页面，重新生成 public 文件。（hexo g 是 hexo generate 的简写)</strong></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><strong>启动本地服务，在 <a href=\"http://localhost:4000/\">http://localhost:4000/</a> 预览效果。（hexo s 是 hexo server 的简写）</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li><strong>部署推送，部署到 github。（hexo d 是 hexo deploy 的简写）</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li><strong>以上连写示例一（清理缓存 + 生成静态页面 + 在本地预览）</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo cl &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li><strong>以上连写示例二（清理缓存 + 生成静态页面 + 部署推送）</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo cl &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"主题更换\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#主题更换\">#</a> 主题更换</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><strong>挑选主题，hexo 官网或 github 下载主题。<a href=\"https://hexo.io/themes/\">（HEXO theme）</a></strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>下载解压，放到自己博客目录下的 themes 文件夹。</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/configuration\">主题配置</a>，修改_config.yml 参数。</strong></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">theme:</span> <span class=\"string\">shoka</span> <span class=\"comment\">#更换主题名称</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight yml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Site修改网站标题、副标题、作者、语言等</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">title:</span> <span class=\"string\">CodingFXJ&#x27;Blog</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">subtitle:</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">description:</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">keywords:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">author:</span> <span class=\"string\">FXJ</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">language:</span> <span class=\"string\">zh-CN</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">timezone:</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>\n<p><strong>其余基本配置 、依赖插件、界面显示、特殊功能配置等，需要查看自己主题的使用说明，按要求设置。</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>超好看主题收藏</strong></p>\n<h6 id=\"matery\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#matery\">#</a> matery</h6>\n<h6 id=\"butterfly\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#butterfly\">#</a> butterfly</h6>\n<h6 id=\"minhow\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#minhow\">#</a> MinHow</h6>\n<h6 id=\"yunyoujun\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#yunyoujun\">#</a> yunyoujun</h6>\n<h6 id=\"yllia\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#yllia\">#</a> yllia</h6>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"博客发布\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#博客发布\">#</a> 博客发布</h3>\n<h4 id=\"新建博客\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#新建博客\">#</a> 新建博客</h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">初始化博客</span><br><span class=\"line\"> hexo init 文件夹名称</span><br><span class=\"line\">新建文章</span><br><span class=\"line\"> hexo new 文章名称 (或者) hexo n 文章名称</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"修改内容\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#修改内容\">#</a> 修改内容</h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">title:</span> <span class=\"comment\">#标题</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">date:</span> <span class=\"comment\">#文章发布日期  年/月/日 时/分/秒 示：2020/12/24 12:10:45</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">tags:</span> <span class=\"comment\">#添加标签</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">HTML</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">Note</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">categories:</span> <span class=\"string\">HTML</span> <span class=\"comment\">#分类</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"文章插入图片\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#文章插入图片\">#</a> 文章插入图片</h4>\n<h6 id=\"markdown语法\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#markdown语法\">#</a> Markdown 语法</h6>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">本地插入方式：</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t![图片信息](/source目录下图片所处文件夹名/图片名)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">网络图片插入：</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t![图片信息](图片地址)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h6 id=\"html语法\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#html语法\">#</a> HTML 语法</h6>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">本地：</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&lt;img src=&quot;/source目录下图片所处文件夹名/图片名&quot; alt=&quot;图片信息&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">网络：</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&lt;img src=&quot;图片地址&quot; alt&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>效果展示：<br>\n<img src=\"http://pic1.win4000.com/m00/43/e4/69301a44acfd7de469f82d360d349fb5.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"文章插图视频\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#文章插图视频\">#</a> 文章插图视频</h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">复制 嵌入代码 到文章，可通过width、height修改播放窗口尺寸\t\t\t</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>效果展示：</p>\n<iframe  width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=37743569&bvid=BV1Mt411D73n&cid=66352604&page=1\" scrolling=\"no\" border=\"0\" frameborder=\"no\" framespacing=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"> </iframe>\n<h4 id=\"音频嵌入\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#音频嵌入\">#</a> 音频嵌入</h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">生成外链播放器，复制 HTML代码</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>效果展示：</p>\n  <iframe frameborder=\"no\" border=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" width=330 height=86 src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=65766&auto=0&height=66\"></iframe>\n<h4 id=\"网址插入\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#网址插入\">#</a> 网址插入</h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Markdown语法</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t[网站名](网址)  \t#[网易云音乐](https://music.163.com/#) 或 markdown快捷键:Ctrl+K</span><br><span class=\"line\">HTML语法</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;a href=&quot;网址&quot;&gt;网站名&lt;/a&gt;    #&lt;a href=&quot;https://music.163.com/#&quot;&gt;网易云音乐&lt;/a&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>​\t\t效果展示：\t\t<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/\">哔哩哔哩</a></p>\n<h4 id=\"一键三连完成发布与查看\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#一键三连完成发布与查看\">#</a> 一键三连完成发布与查看</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>本地查看</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo cl &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>部署到 github</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo cl &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"部署遇到的问题及解决方式\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#部署遇到的问题及解决方式\">#</a> 部署遇到的问题及解决方式</h4>\n<p>hexo d 遇到问题一：删除博客根目录下的.deploy_git 文件，重新部署（  <strong>hexo cl &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d</strong>）</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/20210523134101.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>hexo d 遇到问题二： <code> OpenSSL SSL_read: Connection was reset, errno 10054</code></p>\n<p>解决方法： <code>git config --global http.sslVerify &quot;false&quot;</code></p>\n<h4 id=\"大功告成\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#大功告成\">#</a> 大功告成！</h4>\n",
